# cloud-ui environment configuration.
# Copy to .env.local and fill in. .env.local is gitignored.

# ── API ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Base URL for dc-api. Leave unset in dev to use the Vite proxy
# (configured in vite.config.ts to forward /v1/* to the deployed
# dc-api). Set in production builds, e.g. https://dcapi.lk.internal.wso2.com
# VITE_API_BASE=

# ── Dev-only proxy override ──────────────────────────────────────────
# Override the Vite proxy target. Defaults to the deployed dc-api;
# set to localhost:8080 when running dc-api locally.
# VITE_API_PROXY_TARGET=http://localhost:8080
